);\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/SplitTestOnlyMetadataTask.java:59:                getLogger().error(\"splitTestOnlyMetadata failed for {}: {}\", coordinate, exception.getMessage());\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/SplitTestOnlyMetadataTask.java:64:            throw new GradleException(\"splitTestOnlyMetadata failed for the following coordinates:\\n - \" + String.join(\"\\n - \", failures));\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/SplitTestOnlyMetadataTask.java:74:                            + \"splitTestOnlyMetadata only runs for versions that have their own metadata.\",\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/SplitTestOnlyMetadataTask.java:116:        getLogger().lifecycle(\"splitTestOnlyMetadata completed for {}\", coordinate);\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
